STATE
v.
LEE 2018-1718 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 23, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On review of an order certifying a conflict. The court determines that a conflict exists. Sua sponte, cause held for the decision in 2018-1348, State v. Pendleton, and briefing schedule stayed. Sua sponte, cause consolidated with 2018-1585, State v. Lee.
